#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_company_team
msgid "Livia Sailor"
msgstr "Livia Sailor"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_company_team
msgid ""
"Livia is our head wedding coordinator and stylist, she'll turn any of your "
"ideas into reality, making sure your wedding day is smooth and looks better "
"than anything you have ever seen on Pinterest."
msgstr ""
"Livia is onze leidinggevende weddingplanner en styliste. Ze laat al je "
"ideeën werkelijkheid worden en zorgt ervoor dat je bruiloft vlotjes verloopt "
"en er beter uitziet dan alles wat je ooit op Pinterest hebt gezien."

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Married in 2019"
msgstr "Getrouwd in 2019"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Married in 2020"
msgstr "Getrouwd in 2020"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_image_text_overlap
msgid "OUR MISSION"
msgstr "ONZE MISSIE"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Our goal is to ensure this day will be unforgettable for you and your "
"beloved soulmate."
msgstr ""
"Ons doel is om ervoor te zorgen dat deze dag onvergetelijk wordt voor jou en "
"je geliefde soulmate."

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_freegrid
msgid "PORTFOLIO"
msgstr "PORTFOLIO"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Renewed their vows in 2021"
msgstr "Hernieuwden hun geloften in 2021"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "Rose and Peter"
msgstr "Roos en Peter"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_yes.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thematools"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "They made our big day stree-free and absolutely beautiful!"
msgstr "Ze maakten onze grote dag zonder strubbelingen en absoluut prachtig!"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "They turned our dream into reality with ease and professionalism!"
msgstr ""
"Ze hebben onze droom met gemak en professionaliteit werkelijkheid gemaakt!"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_freegrid
msgid "View all the pictures"
msgstr "Bekijk alle foto's"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_title
msgid "We are two passionate<br/>with years of experience"
msgstr "Wij zijn twee gepassioneerde<br/>met jarenlange ervaring"

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_features
msgid ""
"We help you crafting a personalized wedding menu tailored to your tastes."
msgstr ""
"We helpen je bij het samenstellen van een persoonlijk bruiloftsmenu, "
"afgestemd op jullie smaak."

#. module: theme_yes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_yes.s_features
msgid ""
"We help you discover the ideal location that matches your style and vision."
msgstr ""
"We helpen je de ideale locatie te vinden die past bij je stijl en visie."
